        "flowName": "getPatientProfile",
        "verified": "runtime-precheck",
        "description": "contract.audit requires a runtime report; audit.write is declared and AuditLog.write is called with event PatientProfileRead"
      },
      {
        "kind": "totality",
        "flowName": "getPatientProfile",
        "verified": "runtime-precheck",
        "description": "validate.patientId and PatientsDB.findById use ? (early-return Err(ApiError)); errors map PatientNotFound->NotFound, AccessDenied->Unauthorised; the flow returns Result<Response, ApiError> on every path"
