    "exhaustiveness": "No match arms in the body; fallible calls are made total by ?. The contract.errors block enumerates the full ApiError surface (NotFound, Unauthorised, Internal) with explicit map/expose/redact/audit handling, so every error variant is accounted for. Deny-by-default: only database.read and audit.write are admissible.",
